Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Software
Sub-Industry: Application Software
Stryder Corp., doing business as Handshake, provides software solutions. The Company offers solutions to recruit students and to transform the recruiting experience for college students, career centers, and employers. Handshake operates in the State of California.




