Products Spotlight
Accolade II

Accolade II is a tapered wedge stem that has been designed to fit more patients while accommodating a variety of surgical approaches.1,2* It is the first Morphometric Wedge design. This is characterized by a size specific medial curvature that fits a broad range of bone sizes and shapes found ...
		


Find out more





Products Spotlight
Mobile Bearing Hip™ System

ADM X3 is a large head solution for patients worldwide. Stryker now introduces MDM X3 – the first Modular Mobile Bearing Hip System. The Mobile Bearing Hip System complete with patented1 anatomic monoblock and modular shell options is designed to increase versatility to help orthopaedic ...
		


Find out more





